snippet.title: ARKHAM THOTS
snippet.description:
The purpose of this channel is to teach the youth to respect women and responsibly examine certain non-sexual aspects of DC cartoons.  My videos meaningfully transform the content from simply animation and film to life lessons and education.

I am in no way affiliated with Warner Bros. or DC Comics
